- content_for(:head) do
  = stylesheet_link_tag 'css/pd', media: 'all'

#thanks
  %h1 Thank you for your application.

  %h2
    Code.org and our Regional Partners, where applicable, will review all applications after the application deadline.
    We will provide a status update to all applicants by the end of February 2019.

  %p
    - if @display_regional_partner_reminder
      As a reminder, your Code.org Regional Partner is:
      = @application.regional_partner.name
    - else
      As a reminder, your application is not yet matched to a Code.org Regional Partner.
      If there is a partner in your area, we will send your application to the partner for review.
      If there isn't yet a partner in your area, we will consider your application if we develop a need for facilitators in your region.

  %p
    Due to the volume of applications we receive, we are not able to respond to individual requests for status updates.
    Please contact
    =link_to('facilitators@code.org', 'mailto:facilitators@code.org')
    with all other questions.

  %p
    In the meantime, please visit
    =link_to('https://code.org/yourschool', 'https://code.org/yourschool', target: '_blank')
    and tell us more about what computer science opportunities are available at your school or schools in your area.
    Thank you for supporting computer science for all!
